summary: Moominvalley Picture Disc Vinyl I’ll be honest, when I first heard the Mø song, I thought it was good, but I didn’t feel it was...
caption:
Moominvalley Picture Disc Vinyl

I’ll be honest, when I first heard the Mø song, I thought it was good, but I didn’t feel it was very Moominous. My thoughts on it however, have changed. I love this album! it’s so summery and I think all the artists contributed excellent Moomin inspired tracks. My favourite probably being Tom Odell’s Summer Day.

Just to say as well, I only have the Moomintroll vinyl, but it has a different image on the back, a still of him from the series, so I assume the others do too!

I’d love them to release the score of the series as well because I think it’s beautifully composed!
